    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A generic style, particularly in the context of interior design, characterized by soft, comfortable furnishings incorporating antiques or replicas of antiques reminiscent of 19th-century rural farmhouses or cottages of Britain and the United States.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
